{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a couple of times, even-- but this is, again, another story-- a couple of times one of them, after-- there was-- he came-- he says if I should come to his house, wherever he lived, he would give me a duck-- a live duck.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first time when I was so upset.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way back, there were Polish peasant women standing there in front of this base.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, each one of them needed something, or he-- and here I come with this duck.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started literally attacking me physically-- from whom did you-- I mean, in Polish if they really want to offend you, they call you [POLISH]-- from whom did you steal that duck?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took it away from me, they beat me up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember I was so-- that was really the first time and I was trying to be, you know, sort of behave like a lady about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, aren't you ashamed?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am a Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was born here, I went to school here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I even help when you-- if you come to ask me for some help because I happen to speak German because I finished school already.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were so-- so this was really the first time, that-- and then a very short time later there was a-- a ghetto announced.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to move from this place, and we moved to a part of the ghetto place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this what a time when also they started-- but they were preparing the ghetto, it wasn't so fast.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were building bridges-- Ben told you, maybe, he was-- no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The things which they were doing, you know, that was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
